<!-- ABOUT THE PROJECT -->
## About The Repo

This repo is the exercices about Android mobile development made during the Android Development course.

### Built With


* [Java](https://www.java.com/fr/)
* [Android Studio](https://developer.android.com/studio)



<!-- GETTING STARTED -->
## Getting Started

Instructions for the project setup :
* Clone the repo and open it with Android Studio
* Configure an emulator or something to run it (Run/Debug Configurations and add Android App if there's nothing)

### Prerequisites

* Java
* Android Studio

### Installation


1. Clone the repo
   ```sh
   git clone https://github.com/giornotheme/Android-Development-Labs.git
   ```
2. Open it with Android Studio
3. Run it
